description:
A voluptuous and beautiful mystery woman. She talks like an Oiran (courtesan), and everything she says is erotic. She confronts http://anidb.net/ch65416 [Keiichirou] and http://anidb.net/ch65417 [Kiriko] several times for a particular purpose. Master of kung fu, she uses a giant iron fan.
Source: ANN
name: Houkouin
